	<body>
		<header>
			What will I learn in this unit?
		</header>
		
		<section id="body">
			<img class="rightFloat" src="media/LE_TV_001.jpg" />
			<p class="h1">Leisure activites</p>
			<p class="no-padding">You will...</p>
			<list>
				<listMarkerFormat>
					<ListMarkerFormat fontWeight="normal" paragraphEndIndent="10px" />
				</listMarkerFormat>
				<li><p class="no-padding">listen to people talking about how they spend their free time and decide what their leisure activities are.</p></li>
    			<li><p class="no-padding">read an email describing how someone spends their free time and complete it with appropriate words and phrases.</p></li>
    		</list>
    		
			<p class="h1">Sports, games and equipment</p>
			<p class="no-padding">You will...</p>
			<list>
				<listMarkerFormat>
					<ListMarkerFormat fontWeight="normal" paragraphEndIndent="10px" />
				</listMarkerFormat>
				<li><p class="no-padding">match the names of sports and games to pictures.</p></li>
				<li><p class="no-padding">match equipment to sports and games.</p></li>
				<li><p class="no-padding">do a quiz about sports and games.</p></li>
			</list>
			
		</section>
	</body>
	
